          java.lang.String imageURL
          An URL to an image file for the Medium.

        • description

          java.lang.String description
          A synopsis of the volume. The text of the description is formatted in HTML and includes simple formatting elements, such as b, i, and br tags.

          java.lang.String note
          Any kind of note on the Medium, usually created by the librarian, for instance, regarding the damage status of the book.
